# GitHub Copilot Integration - bGen

**Status:** ✅ Vollständig implementiert
**Datum:** 2025-11-19

---

## 🎯 Übersicht

bGen unterstützt jetzt **drei AI-Provider** für Textgenerierung:
1. **OpenAI** (GPT-Modelle)
2. **Anthropic** (Claude-Modelle)
3. **GitHub Copilot** (GitHub-Modelle mit Copilot-Token) ✨ NEU

---

## 🔧 Implementierung

### Backend-Änderungen

#### 1. Setting Model (`backend/models/Setting.js`)
```javascript
provider: {
  type: String,
  enum: ["openai", "claude", "copilot"], // ✅ copilot hinzugefügt
  default: "openai",
}
```

#### 2. API Client (`backend/utils/apiClient.js`)

**Neue Copilot-Funktionen:**
```javascript
// Initialisierung mit GitHub Token
async function initializeCopilot(apiKey) {
  copilotInstance = axios.create({
    baseURL: "https://api.githubcopilot.com",
    headers: {
      "Authorization": `Bearer ${apiKey}`,
      "Content-Type": "application/json"
    }
  });
}

// Text-Generierung via Copilot Chat API
async function generateWithCopilot(prompt, setting) {
  const response = await copilot.post("/chat/completions", {
    messages: [
      {
        role: "system",
        content: "You are a helpful assistant specialized in generating professional German text for disability insurance reports."
      },
      {
        role: "user",
        content: prompt
      }
    ],
    model: setting.model || "gpt-4o",
    max_tokens: setting.maxTokens || 2000,
    temperature: setting.temperature || 0.7
  });

  return response.data.choices[0].message.content.trim();
}
```

**Erweiterte `generateReport` Funktion:**
```javascript
async function generateReport(prompt, userId) {
  const setting = await getUserSettings(userId);
  const provider = setting.provider || "openai";

  if (provider === "claude") {
    return await generateWithClaude(prompt, setting);
  } else if (provider === "copilot") {
    return await generateWithCopilot(prompt, setting); // ✅ NEU
  } else {
    return await generateWithOpenAI(prompt, setting);
  }
}
```

### Frontend-Änderungen

#### 1. Type Definitions (`src/types/index.ts`)
```typescript
export type AIProvider = 'openai' | 'claude' | 'copilot'; // ✅ copilot hinzugefügt
```

#### 2. Settings Modal (`src/components/SettingsModalNew.tsx`)

**Copilot-Modelle:**
```typescript
const copilotModels = [
  'gpt-4o',
  'gpt-4o-mini',
  'gpt-4',
  'gpt-3.5-turbo',
];
```

**Provider-Auswahl:**
```jsx
<select value={formData.provider} onChange={...}>
  <option value="openai">OpenAI (GPT)</option>
  <option value="claude">Anthropic (Claude)</option>
  <option value="copilot">GitHub Copilot</option> {/* ✅ NEU */}
</select>
```

**Dynamischer Token-Hinweis:**
```jsx
<label>
  {formData.provider === 'copilot' ? 'GitHub Token' : 'API-Schlüssel'}
</label>

<input
  type="password"
  placeholder={
    formData.provider === 'openai' ? 'sk-...' :
    formData.provider === 'claude' ? 'sk-ant-...' :
    'ghp_... oder ghu_...' // ✅ GitHub Token Format
  }
/>

<p className="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
  {formData.provider === 'copilot' ?
   'GitHub Personal Access Token von github.com/settings/tokens mit copilot Scope' :
   // ... andere Provider
  }
</p>
```

